===Etymology 1===
{{etymid|ja|asa}}
{{ja-kanjitab|yomi=k|あさ}}
{{wp|ja:}}
{{wp|Morning}}

From {{inh|ja|ojp|-}}, from {{inh|ja|jpx-pro|*asa}}. Attested in the ''{{w|Man'yōshū}}'' of 759.<ref name="NKD2O-asa">{{R:ja:NKD2O|あさ 【朝】|lid=2002000f6bd37V14Ez0r|kotobank=朝-423925#w-1864538}}</ref>

Historically, a day was split into two halves:
* Afternoon cycle: {{ja-r|朝|あさ}} → {{ja-r|昼|ひる}} → {{ja-r|夕|ゆう}}
* Evening cycle: {{ja-r|夕べ|ゆうべ}} → {{ja-r|宵|よい}} → {{ja-r|夜%中|よ%なか}} → {{ja-r|暁|あかつき}} → {{ja-r|朝|あした|linkto=朝#Etymology 2}}
While ''asa'' and ''ashita'' represent the same time period, ''asa'' was associated with beginning of the afternoon and ''ashita'' was associated with the end of the night. Both terms share an initial ''as-'' and are likely etymologically related.

Beyond Japonic, possibly related to {{cog|okm|아ᄎᆞᆷ〮|tr=àchóm|t=morning}} > {{cog|ko|아침}}. {{w|Alexander Vovin}} believes this is a Koreanic borrowing into Japanese, identifying {{ncog|ja|-}} {{ja-r|つとめて}} as the native Japonic root for "morning" ({{jpx-ref|Vovin 2010, p. 224}}).
* However, {{ja-r|つとめて}} is not attested until the late 800s or early 900s,<ref name="NKD2O-tsutomete">{{R:ja:NKD2O|つとめ‐て
|lid=200202d5dcd6G5Z602lA|kotobank=つとめて-572050#w-2052959}}</ref> although root {{ja-r|夙|つと}} as in {{ja-r|夙に|つと に|[[early]] in the [[morning]]|pos=adverb}} appears in the ''{{w|Man'yōshū}}'' of 759.<ref name="MYS">{{RQ:MYS|18|4111}}</ref>

Alternatively, may be cognate with adjective {{ja-r|浅い|あさい|[[shallow]]; [[early]]}}, verbs {{ja-r|浅せる|あせる|to become [[shallow]]}} and {{ja-r|褪せる|あせる|to [[fade]], to become [[pale]]}}.
* The concepts of "[[shallow]]" and "[[deep]]" are used in other respects relative to time, such as {{ja-r|夜更かし|よふかし|[[stay up|staying up]] [[late]] into the [[night]]}} and {{ja-r|夜%更け|よ%ふけ|very [[late]] at [[night]]}}, where the ''fuk-'' root in both terms is from {{ja-r|深い|ふかい|[[deep]]; [[late]], [[long-lasting]]}}.<ref name="NKDc-asai">{{R:ja:NKD Concise|浅い}}</ref><ref name="DDJS-asai">{{R:Digital-Daijisen|浅い}}</ref><ref name="NKD2O-asai">{{R:ja:NKD2O|あさ・い 【浅】|lid=2002000f93581Qy2C64h|kotobank=浅い-423944#w-1864574}}</ref>

